Package Model

Class Borrow

  • java.lang.Object
    • Model.Serializable
      • Model.Borrow
  • public class Borrow
extends Serializable
    The Borrow class represents a borrowing transaction, containing information about the associated account, book, borrow status, borrow time, and return time.

    This class extends the Serializable class to support serialization.

    Author:
    Darmawan Hanif
